<title>USA: Mark IV Industries completes audio sale.</title>
<headline>Mark IV Industries completes audio sale.</headline>
<dateline>AMHERST, N.Y. 1997-02-11</dateline>
<text>
<p>Mark IV Industries Inc said on Tuesday it completed the sale of Mark IV Audio to an affiliate of Greenwich Street Capital Partners Inc for $156.4 million in cash.</p>
<p>The final price was raised from the $151.5 million previously announced to accommodate changes in Mark IV Audio's balance sheet through the date of closing.</p>
<p>Mark IV Industries said it will use the proceeds to pay down bank debt, and eventually to help it make acquisitions and possibly to repurchase company stock.</p>
